title: Launch Button then NOTHING
body:
After bringing up the launcher, I select the launch button and the login screen never appears. I have tried repair, compatibility, restarting, admin, reinstalling, and wifi reset. What else can i try?

SOLVED: process windows bundle was keeping it from launching.

replies.body:
There could be a number of local network settings that could be causing this. If your connection to the login server is not stable, it can prevent the login screen from even appearing. As a first step, I recommend working through the steps in our [connection troubleshooting guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) to ensure your local configuration is good.

Let me know if those steps helped.

I found my problem, Windows Bundle in processes was locking it from launching.
